data.description: Motivated sellers!!!! Huge detached garage in back of the giant lot. This home is very light, bright and spacious! The front room has huge windows letting a ton of natural light in, perfect for the green thumb enthusiasts. The nicely spaced kitchen has plenty of storage that leads to a unique, chill nook that just asks for a snuggly chair and book.  Large back room with wet bar for entertaining or great for cozy nights sitting next to the wood fireplace. Space for RV on the side too!
